{"tid":1441010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有[撤回]送中修例，遊行抗爭可能延至明年71","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:53:56.000Z","uid":299594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1fdefe17212c6015ce8c5ac8d1edb17fe70e47","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"由於林奠沒有返去立法局正式[撤回]送中修例，至明年7月1日前，她仍然有機會開一次會、在一日内完成修例。她用的[壽終正寢]、[the bill is dead]並不是法律名詞，那是沒有法律效力的。當你細心聽她的speech, 你會留意到她用了&quot;will&quot;幾次去描術修例如何在明年71expire，這明確說出<strong>[送中修例仍然存在]</strong>。她說立法局開會時間表至明年71沒有修例事項， 但是<strong>會議項目和時間表是可以改的</strong>。因此，遊行抗爭有機會延至明年7月1日。<br />\n大家要有心理準備，要打持久戰， 要保存實力呀。已經有600個義士被拉咗， 再損兵折將落去會大大减弱抗爭能力。<br />\n由今日開始， 不被捕、 不受傷、不流血、不犧牲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d96a77722fcb88b3c1dbc5d508f0027d26b684","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da2917e7e9367701dec96b1e4934b6ff5dd1786f","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9175ee84e06ac42856cabee01f6a293ba7e386b4","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"447c1b6e7be21961e8331ffb8886f510013e3950","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a198f9a7c8928c39d39bcdb9d2af5344e53c076","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a6e49118a5c7eafedef0a80f8b4d4a03ef6e5661","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2e67793e976a224195605b196b05a1e54e7b127","tid":1441010,"uid":299594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"pus